Research has shown that the red edge band has extremely high sensitivity in vegetation monitoring31. In areas with vegetation, the red edge peak can be used as an indicator to assess severe water stress. In order to effectively reduce the disturbance of vegetation on soil moisture content in mining area, a new ReMPDI was constructed by using the Red Edge band. The calculation method is as shown in Formula (4):4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
